data.description:
Welcome to your new home! This charming single-family residence is now available for rent, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. Here are the key features that make this property stand out:
Location:
Situated in a desirable neighborhood Riverbend, Sanford this home offers proximity to Galileo School, New Publix shopping centers, 30 mins from Daytona . Major highways are all nearby. 

Bedrooms:
Three generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for your family or guests.

Bathrooms:
Two well-appointed bathrooms 

Kitchen:
A fully equipped kitchen with modern appliances awaits the culinary enthusiast in you.

Living Spaces:
Enjoy the open and inviting living spaces, perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing with loved ones.

Outdoor Area:
The property boasts a private backyard or patio, ideal for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the fresh air.
Parking:

Convenient parking spaces, including a garage or driveway, make coming home a breeze.

Amenities:
Onsite Playground and Swimming Pool.
Lease Terms:

Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Schedule a viewing today to experience the comfort and charm that await you in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home.

Tenant is responsible for lawn and utilities.
